Li ya ambaci gasar fasahar gwamnatin Amurka ta baya, kamar Gasar Robotics Challenge na Hukumar Cibiyar Bincike ta Tsaro, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a yi gasar ta gaba, don taimakawa wajen gano mutane na gaba.
