Almanac: wanda ya ƙirƙira ma'aunin Geiger
Kuma yanzu shafi na mu na "Sunday Morning" Almanac: Shekaru 136 da suka shige, a ranar 30 ga Satumba, 1882, kuma daga baya, a wannan rana ne aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na nan gaba Jonas William "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta ganowa da kuma auna radiation, wannan shine abin da ya kai ga gano na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
Tun daga lokacin, ilimin kimiyya na yau da kullun, Geiger counter ya zama babban al'adun al'adu, kamar yadda Roy Rogers da Dale Evans suka yi a cikin fim ɗin 1950 "Bells of Coronado" wanda ke nuna masana kimiyya masu kama da cowboys:
Mutum: "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan shi ne Geiger counter, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen gano abubuwa masu guba kamar uranium.
Idan ka saka wannan na'urar, za ka iya jin sauti na nukiliya da ke fitowa daga salts ta hanyar hasken rana".
Evans: "Za ka iya cewa suna fitowa yanzu!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ya cika shekara 63.
Amma abin da ya sa aka kira shi da sunansa ya rayu har abada.
