Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai yi aiki a wani sabon fim na Sam Shepherd mai suna True West, wanda ya yi magana game da wani mai shirya fim da ɗan'uwansa da ya yi fashi.
A kwanan nan, ɗan wasan ya bayyana cewa mafi kyawun sakamako na Game of Thrones shine kyautar matarsa Rose.
