John English ya Sake Yajin - Aikin Bincike na Rowan Atkinson
An riga an yi al'ada cewa kowane sabon fim na Birtaniya zai nuna tasirin Brexit, kuma hakan ya shafi harkar fim na Johnny English, wanda aka fara a 2003 a matsayin Johnny English, kuma aka sake farfado da shi a 2011 a matsayin Johnny English Reborn.
Za a yi wa kanmu ba'a game da yadda muke da ƙima a matsayin sabon damar fitar da kayayyaki na ƙasar?
A kowane hali, Johnny English, wanda ba shi da kyau, yana da lasisin sake sabuntawa na biyu - sunansa ya nuna cewa yana da zane-zane mai ban sha'awa don masu kallo a yankunan da ba na Turanci ba.
Tabbas shi ɗan leƙen asiri ne wanda duk da irin wannan ban mamaki na ban dariya, ya ɗan yi kama da Mr. Bean, kuma ɗan ƙaramin mutumin nan ya ba da gudummawa ga waƙar da aka yi da Charities of Fire a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London ta 2012.
Wannan hali ya kara da cewa Atkinson ya dogara ne da matafiyi da kuma wani baƙon ɗan ƙasa wanda ya taɓa yin fim ɗin tallan talabijin na Barclays wanda yanzu an manta da shi, yana ƙara rikice-rikice.
Akwai wasu abubuwa masu ban sha'awa a cikin wannan sabon fim na JE.
Na fi son lokacin da John English yake tafiya zuwa jirgi mai saukar ungulu da rigar yaƙi na zamanin da, kuma ya ga ƙafar fan ɗin tana buga ƙwalƙwalwar sa a kan kansa.
An ga baiwar da Atkins ya samu na ban dariya amma, ba'a da amfani sosai, kuma musamman a cikin yanayin cewa "mai tsanani" alamun fim kamar 007 da Mission Impossible yanzu sun haɗa da gaskiya a matsayin ɓangare.
Kamar dai ba a shirya wa yara ba ne, amma ga manya, kuma na ga cewa Johnny English ba shi da basira da kuma hankali kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a fim ɗin da ba shi da sauti.
Yanzu, babban abin da ya sa aka yi wannan magana shi ne cewa Birtaniya tana cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan damfara na intanet ya shiga cikin wani babban asirin yanar gizo na hukumar leken asiri ta Burtaniya, ya gano duk wani wakili da ke aiki a Birtaniya, ya kuma ba da labarin yadda aka yi wannan wakili ya yi aiki - wani aiki da Kevin Alden bai cika ba.
Wani abu na ƙarshe da za a yi wa mai son faɗa da kuma wanda ya riga ya fara faduwa a siyasa shi ne: Emma Thompson ta yi wasa mai kyau kamar Teresa-May, amma ba ta da sauran abin da za ta yi a cikin labarin.
Masu ba ta shawara a kan harkokin leken asiri sun gaya mata cewa idan ta samu labarin wani da ke yin leken asiri, za ta bukaci wani da ya yi ritaya ya zo.
Kuma wannan yana nufin cewa Johnny English, wanda yake malamin makaranta a wani babban masallaci, yana koyar da darasi na waje-karshen yadda za a zama jami'in leken asiri: akwai wasu abubuwa masu ban dariya a nan, domin ya mai da makarantar Ingila makarantar leken asiri ta rock-type.
An sake kiran Ingilishi zuwa White Hall don sanar da gaggawa kuma an sake ganawa da abokin aikinsa na dogon lokaci, Bo, wanda Bel Miller ya buga.
Bo yanzu ya yi aure, ya auri kwamandan jirgin ruwa mai ruwa, rawar da take takawa da rawa da take cinye kwarewar wani mai fasaha kamar Vicky Pepperdine.
A cikin kowane Majestic Secret Service, Batman da Robin suna yin mummunan kuskure, suna fuskantar kyawawan mata masu kisan kai na Olga Kurilenko, Ofelia Bulletova.
A lokacin, Firayim Minista ya shiga cikin wani mummunan hali na wani mai karamar fasaha mai yawa wanda ya yi iƙirarin cewa zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Burtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro wanda Jake Lacey ya buga.
English da Bo sun fara tafiya mai ban dariya: suna kama da masu jiran aiki suna ƙona gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai ban sha'awa; suna rikicewa yayin da suke yin safarar kansu daga jirgin ruwan Volta mai tsada; kuma English ya yi rikici yayin da yake ƙoƙarin sanya kansa a kan kayan aikin gaskiya na gaskiya don sanin abubuwan da ke cikin gidan Volta.
