Jam'iyyar Labor ta musanta cewa Birtaniya na shirin yin aiki kwana hudu a mako da kuma biyan albashi na kwana biyar.
Jeremy Corbyn ya ce jam'iyyar Labour tana tunanin sauya tsarin aiki na kwanaki hudu a mako da kuma biyan albashi na kwanaki biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta ce tana son masu kamfanin su yi amfani da kudaden da suka samu daga juyin juya halin kere kere (AI) don ba ma'aikata karin rana.
Wannan zai ba ma'aikatan hutu na kwana uku amma ba za a rage musu albashi ba.
A cewar majiyoyin, wannan ra'ayin ya 'dace' a cikin tsarin tattalin arziki da kuma manufofin jam'iyyar na karkatar da kasar zuwa ga bukatun ma'aikata.
