Menene bikin Global Citizen kuma shin sun yi wani abu don kawar da talauci?
A ranar Asabar mai zuwa, za a yi bikin bikin Global Citizen Festival a New York, wanda ya ƙunshi taurari masu ban sha'awa, kuma manufar bikin ita ce kawar da talauci a duniya.
A wannan shekara ta bakwai na bikin Global Citizen, dubban miliyoyin mutane za su taru a filin wasa mai suna Great Lawn na Central Park ba wai kawai don jin daɗin ayyukan masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Sean Mendes ba, amma don yada ainihin manufar bikin, wanda shine kawar da talauci a duniya ta 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani nau'i ne na Global Poverty Project, wani rukunin masu ba da shawara na duniya da ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar haɓaka yawan masu fafutukar kawar da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta na taron (idan ba kwa son siyan tikitin VIP), masu sauraron taron dole ne su aiwatar da wasu ayyuka ko jerin "ayyuka" kamar yin aikin sa kai don yada manufar kawar da duniya, aika imel ga shugaban duniya, yin waya, ko kuma duk wata hanyar da ta dace.
Amma da yake muna da shekaru 12 da za mu cim ma burinmu, yaya Global Citizen ya yi nasara?
Tunani na yin waƙoƙi kyauta ga jama'a, hanya ce ta gaskiya ta sa mutane su ɗauki mataki ko kuma wani nau'i ne na abin da ake kira "clicktivism" - inda mutane suke tunanin cewa yin rajistar takarda ta kan layi ko aika tweets na iya kawo canji?
Global Citizen ta ce tun shekara ta 2011 masu goyon bayanta sun yi fiye da "aiki" miliyan 19 don dalilai daban-daban.
Ya ce ayyukansu sun taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su ba da alkawura da tsare-tsare na dala tiriliyan 37 ko fiye, wanda zai shafi mutane sama da biliyan 225 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, wannan rukunin ya nuna alkawura da sanarwar 390 da suka samo asali daga ayyukansu, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 1 aka riga aka rarraba ko tara.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa, kudaden da aka samu sun shafi rayukan mutane kusan miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da Power of Nutrition, wani hadin gwiwar masu saka jari da masu shirya shirye-shirye a Burtaniya, wanda "ke taimaka wa yara ƙanana su ci gaba zuwa cikakkiyar damar su", kuma wanda bayan karɓar tweets sama da 4,700 daga 'yan ƙasa a duniya, ya yi alkawarin ba da dala miliyan 35 ga ƙasar don kawar da rashin abinci mai gina jiki a Rwanda.
