An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin ruwan yakin Jamus
Jaridar ta ruwaito cewa, sabon jirgin ruwan na Jamus ya kamata a fara aiki a shekarar 2014 domin maye gurbin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma saboda rashin tsari da kuma tsadar farashi, ba za a fara ba har sai a kalla shekara mai zuwa.
Jaridar Die Zeit ta ruwaito wani mai magana da yawun Sojoji, cewa an dage aikin manyan jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg-class, Ryland-Fage, zuwa farkon watanni shida na 2019.
